    "e55bedd4361d5fe6": {
      "id": "e55bedd4361d5fe6",
      "text": "### The Human\n- **Name:** Gianluca Kühne\n- **Location:** Switzerland-based (FHNW, Bern), currently traveling in Colombia\n- **Studies:** Social work student, 10th semester, Hochschule für Soziale Arbeit FHNW\n- **Matrikel-Nr.:** 21-472-519\n- **Language:** English (mit mir) / German (thesis)\n- **Style:** Compact, scientific, dry wit, no emojis",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 14,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.299965",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a6fbc3b4ed912590": {
      "id": "a6fbc3b4ed912590",
      "text": "### BA Thesis (Aktuell: Woche 1 abgeschlossen)\n- **Title:** \"Die internationale Soziale Arbeit im globalen Bildungskontext — Postkoloniale und hegemoniesensitive Analyse internationaler Verschränkungen\"\n- **Institution:** FHNW, Hochschule für Soziale Arbeit\n- **Due:** April 2026 (Bern)\n- **Status:** ~45% complete, Woche 1 (NZ empirische Analyse) abgeschlossen, Woche 2 in Arbeit\n- **Progress:** 2,150 Wörter Woche 1 (Ziel: 1,500), drei-Linsen-Analyse (postkolonial, Hegemonie, epistemische Gerechtigkeit)\n- **Tags:** `#ba-thesis` `#active` `#high` `#writing` `#social-work` `#education`",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 22,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.299998",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "7aaab956b26f57bb": {
      "id": "7aaab956b26f57bb",
      "text": "### System Konfiguration (Aktuell)\n- **Swap:** 2GB swapfile (persistent)\n- **Model:** anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6 (direct) - schneller als OpenRouter\n- **Gateway:** Port 18789, entrosana.com access enabled\n- **Session policy:** maxConcurrent: 2 (Main + Telegram), Session-Bereinigung implementiert\n- **Memory:** E5-small-v2 embeddings (296 chunks, memory files only), LangGraph-E5 Sync operational, expansion to config/projects planned\n- **Disk:** Root 73% (8.3G free), /data 44% (27G free)",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 30,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300025",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "222b641a0ec288cf": {
      "id": "222b641a0ec288cf",
      "text": "### Policy Updates (Relevant)\n- **Telegram:** groupPolicy: \"allowlist\" (leer → Gruppen-Nachrichten fallen durch)\n- **Heartbeat:** Moltbook (9 AM UTC), LangGraph (8 PM UTC), Async Queue processing\n- **Audio policy:** TTS + NO_REPLY only, no duplicates\n- **Session policy:** Eine Main (Dashboard), eine Telegram, Sub-Agenten temporär",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 36,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300044",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c029792757355955": {
      "id": "c029792757355955",
      "text": "## ⚙️ System- & Identitätskonfiguration (komprimiert)",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 38,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300053",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "6172d0ae9ccdcb8b": {
      "id": "6172d0ae9ccdcb8b",
      "text": "### Security Status (03-2026)\n- **Warnings (2):** gateway.auth_no_rate_limit, gateway.nodes.deny_commands_ineffective\n- **Info:** attack_surface open=0, allowlist=1, personal assistant trust model\n- **Hardening:** UFW + iptables (port 18789 → localhost), API encryption (AES-256), SSH via Tailscale",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 43,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300070",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c1a1ef74878ba992": {
      "id": "c1a1ef74878ba992",
      "text": "### Infrastructure (gekürzt)\n- **EBS Volume (01-03):** +50GB gp3 → /data, Audio-Transcription (Whisper) enabled\n- **Disk Optimization (02-03):** Symlinks /.cache/.local/node_modules/go → /data, root 46% → 17GB free\n- **Cleanup:** 5-day archive, 20-day delete retention, daily cleanup script ready",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 48,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300088",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "54deccf56eaecbdb": {
      "id": "54deccf56eaecbdb",
      "text": "### Model Integration\n- **Primary:** Claude Sonnet 4-6 (stable)\n- **Fallback:** Open Router Claude Sonnet 4-6 (Telegram rate limits)\n- **Issue:** DeepSeek API \"Missing reasoning_content field\" → switched to Claude\n- **Multi-Model:** Orchestrator skill (task decomposition, model selection, workflow coordination)",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 54,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300106",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8d03d6803d197f77": {
      "id": "8d03d6803d197f77",
      "text": "### Lessons Learned (Essenz)\n1. **Heartbeat:** Nur bei exaktem Prompt HEARTBEAT_OK, sonst sofort antworten\n2. **Config changes:** Simulieren/testen → Ergebnis zeigen → Permission fragen\n3. **Memory:** AEAP für API-Effizienz (caching, lazy evaluation, batching, context pruning)\n4. **Integration:** \"Don't fight OpenClaw, work with it\" → standalone solutions + HTTP bridges\n5. **Session:** Main (Dashboard) + Telegram only, Sub-Agenten temporär mit Labels",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 61,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300128",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "57dcb10d4780ed37": {
      "id": "57dcb10d4780ed37",
      "text": "### Async Agent Pattern\n- **Problem:** Session-fragile operations break on termination\n- **Solution:** Externalized state (JSONL queues) + heartbeat processing\n- **Timeouts:** Claude messages (120s), Background jobs (600s), API calls (service-specific)\n- **Integration:** HEARTBEAT.md task \"every heartbeat\"",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 67,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.300146",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "49a5eee249ff0158": {
      "id": "49a5eee249ff0158",
