    "b5d6fade274f77fe": {
      "id": "b5d6fade274f77fe",
      "text": "### **Verbose Mode Explanation**\n- **23:38 UTC**: Explained \"verbose\" mode to Gianluca\n- **Definition**: Detailed output with extra information for debugging\n- **Examples**: \n  - `sudo ufw status verbose` (shows default policies, logging settings)\n  - `curl -v` (shows HTTP headers, SSL handshake)\n  - `git status -v` (shows staged changes diff)\n- **Use cases**: Troubleshooting, learning tool behavior, detailed analysis\n- **Rule of thumb**: Normal mode for quick checks, verbose for debugging",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 443,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.302234",
