      "text": "### **Technical Communication Style**\n- **Approach**: Clear, educational explanations of technical concepts\n- **Method**: Simple definitions → concrete examples → practical applications\n- **Goal**: Empower user to understand and use tools effectively\n- **Observation**: Gianluca asks precise technical questions about tool behavior\n\n**Timestamp**: 02-03-2026 23:44 UTC (18:44 Bogotá)\n**Status**: System stable, dashboard operational, knowledge sharing in progress",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
