    "17d58bc4e0ba54d0": {
      "id": "17d58bc4e0ba54d0",
      "text": "### **E5-small-v2 Embedding Engine Implementation**\n- **23:44 UTC**: Discussed E5-small-v2 as embedding engine choice\n- **Decision**: Proceed with E5-small-v2 implementation\n- **Rationale**: Good balance of performance (118M params), multilingual support, memory efficiency\n- **Comparison**: Better than all-MiniLM-L6-v2 for semantic understanding, smaller than e5-base-v2",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
