      "text": "#### **Installation Progress:**\n- **23:48 UTC**: Successfully installed sentence-transformers and torch in virtual environment\n- **Virtual environment**: `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/.venv-embeddings`\n- **Verification**: `✅ Sentence Transformers installed successfully`\n- **Dependencies**: sentence-transformers-5.2.3, torch-2.10.0, transformers-5.2.0",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
