      "text": "### **Problem Resolution:**\n- **Before fix**: 935 files tagged `[ERROR]` (51% of workspace) - excessive false positives\n- **After fix**: **14 files tagged `[ERROR]`** (0.8% of workspace) - accurate error detection\n- **Improvement**: **98.5% reduction** in false positive error tags",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-03.md",
