    "3d8228b2d9e26783": {
      "id": "3d8228b2d9e26783",
      "text": "## Overview\n\nConnect your OpenClaw dashboard to an external website via HTTPS with proper security, SSL certificates, and firewall configuration. This skill handles the complete setup from local gateway to public website access.",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 12,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308519",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "ddd65b000fd55e75": {
      "id": "ddd65b000fd55e75",
      "text": "## 3-Layer Firewall Architecture",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308530",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "293a1deeba754574": {
      "id": "293a1deeba754574",
      "text": "### 1. AWS Security Group (EC2 Level)\n- **Port 443**: Allow `0.0.0.0/0` (HTTPS from anywhere)\n- **Port 18789**: Allow specific IPs or `0.0.0.0/0`",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 39,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308541",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "dcbe7c4a731103e2": {
      "id": "dcbe7c4a731103e2",
      "text": "### 2. AWS Network ACL (Subnet Level - STATEFUL)\n- **INBOUND**: Must allow destination port (18789 after proxy)\n- **OUTBOUND**: Must allow ephemeral ports (1024-65535) for responses\n- **Critical**: NACLs are stateless - need separate inbound AND outbound rules",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 44,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308557",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "341b5566e5f9e652": {
      "id": "341b5566e5f9e652",
      "text": "### 3. Instance Firewall (UFW)\n- **Port 443**: `sudo ufw allow 443/tcp`\n- **Port 18789**: `sudo ufw allow 18789/tcp`\n- **Default**: `deny (incoming)` - must explicitly allow ports",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 49,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308569",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
