    "f33b2ad4764d9a6f": {
      "id": "f33b2ad4764d9a6f",
      "text": "## Troubleshooting Guide",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 522,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308802",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "05a57e8bec6d5ed9": {
      "id": "05a57e8bec6d5ed9",
      "text": "### Quick Reference Table\n\n| Symptom | Likely Cause | Solution |\n|---------|-------------|----------|\n| 502 Bad Gateway | Gateway not running | `openclaw gateway restart` |\n| 504 Timeout | Firewall blocking | Check all 3 firewall layers |\n| SSL errors | Certificate issues | `sudo certbot renew` |\n| WebSocket disconnect | Headers missing | Verify NGINX WebSocket config |\n| Can't connect externally | NACL blocking | Check AWS Network ACL outbound rules |",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 532,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308824",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4ac29a849a3de6e8": {
      "id": "4ac29a849a3de6e8",
      "text": "### Step-by-Step Debugging\n1. **Start local**: `curl http://localhost:18789/`\n2. **Check NGINX**: `curl -k https://localhost/ -H \"Host: entrosana.com\"`\n3. **Check public**: `curl -I https://entrosana.com/`\n4. **Check firewall**: `sudo ufw status verbose`\n5. **Check NACL**: AWS Console → VPC → Network ACLs\n6. **Check logs**: `sudo tail -f /var/log/nginx/error.log`",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 540,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308844",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "08eacd23fcdb43d0": {
      "id": "08eacd23fcdb43d0",
      "text": "## Maintenance Schedule",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 542,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308851",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4b9fc3ad8fbd0000": {
      "id": "4b9fc3ad8fbd0000",
      "text": "### Daily\n- Check dashboard accessibility\n- Monitor error logs\n- Verify SSL certificate validity",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 547,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308860",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8964697a6da50411": {
      "id": "8964697a6da50411",
      "text": "### Weekly\n- Review connection statistics\n- Check for security updates\n- Backup configuration",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 552,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308869",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "ea33b7ab938c25f2": {
      "id": "ea33b7ab938c25f2",
      "text": "### Monthly\n- Renew SSL certificate (auto)\n- Review firewall rules\n- Update OpenClaw and NGINX",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 557,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308878",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "5c22296931a2bc80": {
      "id": "5c22296931a2bc80",
      "text": "### Common Configurations\n- **Single domain**: entrosana.com → OpenClaw dashboard\n- **Subdomain**: dashboard.entrosana.com → OpenClaw\n- **Path-based**: entrosana.com/dashboard → OpenClaw\n- **Multiple instances**: Load balancing across multiple OpenClaw gateways",
      "source": "skills/dashboard-website-connection/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 565,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308893",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "f2a8312bcd6bf4a5": {
      "id": "f2a8312bcd6bf4a5",
      "text": "---\nname: multimedia-processing\ndescription: \"Process audio, images, and video files. Use when: (1) User sends audio messages that need transcription, (2) Images require description or OCR, (3) Video files need processing, (4) Multimedia content needs analysis or conversion.\"\n---\n\n# Multimedia Processing",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 7,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308968",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "0757338741f2c896": {
      "id": "0757338741f2c896",
      "text": "## Overview\n\nThis skill provides tools and workflows for handling multimedia files (audio, images, video) when OpenClaw agents can't process them directly. It includes practical scripts for common tasks and fallback strategies.",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 11,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.308983",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4513cfe7046da7c8": {
      "id": "4513cfe7046da7c8",
      "text": "### When You Receive Multimedia Files\n\n1. **Identify file type:** Check extension (.ogg, .jpg, .mp4, etc.)\n2. **Read metadata:** Use `file` command or FFprobe\n3. **Choose processing method:** Based on available tools\n4. **Provide results or alternatives:** Transcript, description, or conversion",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 20,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309000",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "3e3b54c0df481bd2": {
      "id": "3e3b54c0df481bd2",
      "text": "### Transcription Methods\n\n**1. Local Whisper (Recommended if installed)**\n\n**2. FFmpeg Conversion (Fallback)**\n\n**3. API-Based (OpenAI, Google Cloud)**\nSee `references/audio_apis.md` for API setup.",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 45,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309015",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "980a02793eb2d5e4": {
      "id": "980a02793eb2d5e4",
      "text": "### Audio Analysis Scripts\n\n- `scripts/audio_info.py`: Extract metadata and basic info\n- `scripts/transcribe_audio.py`: Attempt multiple transcription methods\n- `scripts/convert_audio.py`: Format conversion utilities",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 51,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309028",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "cb9209d4e8350f1a": {
      "id": "cb9209d4e8350f1a",
      "text": "### Basic Image Analysis\n\n**1. File Information**\n\n**2. OCR (Optical Character Recognition)**\n\n**3. Image Description (AI-based)**\nRequires vision-capable API (OpenAI GPT-4V, Claude 3.5, etc.)",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 77,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309042",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "19a59e12de36e8f9": {
      "id": "19a59e12de36e8f9",
      "text": "### Image Analysis Scripts\n\n- `scripts/image_info.py`: Extract metadata and dimensions\n- `scripts/ocr_image.py`: Perform OCR on images\n- `scripts/convert_image.py`: Format conversion and resizing",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 83,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309055",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c162915fa18e70c8": {
      "id": "c162915fa18e70c8",
      "text": "### Basic Video Operations\n\n**1. Extract Frames**\n\n**2. Get Video Information**\n\n**3. Convert Formats**",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 106,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309066",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e355db6f775226cc": {
      "id": "e355db6f775226cc",
      "text": "### Video Analysis Scripts\n\n- `scripts/video_info.py`: Extract video metadata\n- `scripts/extract_frames.py`: Extract frames at intervals\n- `scripts/convert_video.py`: Format conversion",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 112,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309077",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "96b171bf741ed680": {
      "id": "96b171bf741ed680",
      "text": "### Workflow 1: Audio Message Processing",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 125,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309085",
