    "812948fc68b2a551": {
      "id": "812948fc68b2a551",
      "text": "### Issue: \"Command not found\"\n**Solution:** Install missing tools:",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 164,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309108",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "14832232360c4cd0": {
      "id": "14832232360c4cd0",
      "text": "### Issue: File format not supported\n**Solution:** Convert to standard format:\n- Audio: WAV or MP3 (16kHz mono recommended)\n- Images: JPEG or PNG\n- Video: MP4 (H.264/AAC)",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 170,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309119",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "f1021f4ca355d3ad": {
      "id": "f1021f4ca355d3ad",
      "text": "### Issue: Poor quality results\n**Solutions:**\n- Audio: Increase sample rate, reduce noise\n- Images: Improve resolution, adjust contrast\n- OCR: Pre-process images (deskew, binarize)",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 176,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309130",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "2fd0e7181f68bb47": {
      "id": "2fd0e7181f68bb47",
      "text": "## Integration with OpenClaw",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 178,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309136",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "00c5e3dc64515c74": {
      "id": "00c5e3dc64515c74",
      "text": "### Automatic Processing\nConfigure OpenClaw to automatically process incoming media:",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 190,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309145",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8b91db02b4fc4608": {
      "id": "8b91db02b4fc4608",
      "text": "### Fallback Strategies\n1. **Primary:** Use installed tools\n2. **Secondary:** Convert and provide metadata\n3. **Tertiary:** Suggest manual processing",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 195,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309156",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "94732464ac0a21b2": {
      "id": "94732464ac0a21b2",
      "text": "## References\n\n- `references/audio_apis.md`: API setup for speech-to-text\n- `references/image_apis.md`: Vision API configurations\n- `references/tool_installation.md`: Installation guides for multimedia tools\n- `references/file_formats.md`: Supported formats and conversions",
      "source": "skills/multimedia-processing/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 202,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.309171",
      "embedding_shape": [
