    "23b7f9bdfd729ae9": {
      "id": "23b7f9bdfd729ae9",
      "text": "## Security Considerations\n\n1. **SSH Security:**\n   - Use key-based authentication\n   - Consider changing default port\n   - Implement fail2ban\n\n2. **Terminal Sharing:**\n   - Termius links contain session credentials\n   - Share links securely",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 217,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310523",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "516911ec6ba3f2d9": {
      "id": "516911ec6ba3f2d9",
      "text": "- Revoke access when done\n\n3. **Web Interfaces:**\n   - OpenClaw UI has authentication\n   - Memory visualization may be public\n   - Consider firewall rules",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 224,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310534",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
