    "a1ed406787ccce2e": {
      "id": "a1ed406787ccce2e",
      "text": "## Future Enhancements\n\n1. **WebSocket Terminal Server**\n   - Real-time terminal sharing\n   - Multiple concurrent sessions\n   - Access control\n\n2. **API Gateway**\n   - REST API for terminal access\n   - Claude Code API endpoint",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 272,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310569",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "2a0739f7085e1bd9": {
      "id": "2a0739f7085e1bd9",
      "text": "- Session management\n\n3. **Integration with OpenClaw**\n   - Native terminal tool\n   - Session spawning with PTY\n   - Better Claude integration",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 279,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310580",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "f844ebf1d2dd9802": {
      "id": "f844ebf1d2dd9802",
      "text": "## References\n\n- Termius Documentation: https://termius.com/help\n- OpenClaw Gateway: `openclaw gateway --help`\n- Claude Code: `claude --help`\n- SSH Configuration: `/etc/ssh/sshd_config`",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 286,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310593",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e0d30a103af6e62d": {
      "id": "e0d30a103af6e62d",
      "text": "## Quick Start\n\n1. **For SSH access:**\n\n2. **For Claude conversation:**\n\n3. **For Termius sharing:**\n   - Use Termius app with provided link\n   - Join multiplayer session\n   - Terminal access shared",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 302,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310606",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "9dd67ae77f5217ca": {
      "id": "9dd67ae77f5217ca",
      "text": "4. **For web interface:**\n   - Open browser to `http://172.31.14.61:18789/`\n   - Use OpenClaw Control UI\n   - May require gateway token",
      "source": "skills/external-terminal-access/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 307,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310617",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
