    "432c6b3c270a394a": {
      "id": "432c6b3c270a394a",
      "text": "### Telegram Bot Integration\nWhen audio is received via Telegram:\n1. Check if Whisper is installed\n2. Transcribe automatically\n3. Send transcript back to user",
