      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "fad2276fa543ee85": {
      "id": "fad2276fa543ee85",
      "text": "### Speed vs Accuracy Trade-off\n- **tiny:** ~32x realtime, lowest accuracy\n- **base:** ~16x realtime, good for most cases\n- **small:** ~4x realtime, better accuracy\n- **medium:** ~1x realtime, high accuracy\n- **large:** ~0.5x realtime, highest accuracy",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 165,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310820",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c9301f3f77c9b13f": {
      "id": "c9301f3f77c9b13f",
      "text": "### Hardware Acceleration",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 177,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310826",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c9f24e88a7d9e8b9": {
      "id": "c9f24e88a7d9e8b9",
      "text": "### `scripts/transcribe.py`\nMain transcription script with options:\n- Model selection\n- Language detection/specification\n- Output formats (txt, srt, vtt, json)\n- Batch processing",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 186,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310838",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "510f44806e7a6a6c": {
      "id": "510f44806e7a6a6c",
      "text": "### `scripts/install_whisper.py`\nComplete installation script:\n- Checks dependencies\n- Installs Whisper and FFmpeg\n- Tests installation\n- Creates aliases",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 193,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310849",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "b5d22d6993a45fb0": {
      "id": "b5d22d6993a45fb0",
      "text": "### `scripts/batch_transcribe.py`\nBatch processing:\n- Process multiple files\n- Parallel processing\n- Progress tracking\n- Error handling",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 200,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310859",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a5dfe0d8718f4b82": {
      "id": "a5dfe0d8718f4b82",
      "text": "### `scripts/audio_cleaner.py`\nPre-process audio:\n- Noise reduction\n- Normalization\n- Format conversion\n- Silence removal",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 207,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310868",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "5ce3489f087a523c": {
      "id": "5ce3489f087a523c",
      "text": "## Comparison with API Services",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310873",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8b45efac96ff85ca": {
      "id": "8b45efac96ff85ca",
      "text": "### Local Whisper Advantages\n- **Privacy:** No data leaves your system\n- **Cost:** Free after installation\n- **Offline:** Works without internet\n- **Control:** Full control over processing",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 215,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310885",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "1fa65aad45024fd6": {
      "id": "1fa65aad45024fd6",
      "text": "### API Service Advantages  \n- **No installation:** Ready to use\n- **Maintenance:** No updates needed\n- **Scalability:** Handles any load\n- **Features:** Additional capabilities",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 221,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310896",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "f4c44d2d3ab0c0aa": {
      "id": "f4c44d2d3ab0c0aa",
      "text": "## When to Use This vs API\n\n**Use local Whisper when:**\n- Privacy is critical\n- You have many files to process\n- Internet is unreliable\n- You want one-time cost (installation)\n\n**Use API when:**\n- Quick setup needed",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 231,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310909",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "29b7f785cb3aed5e": {
      "id": "29b7f785cb3aed5e",
      "text": "- Don't want to manage installations\n- Need advanced features\n- Have budget for per-minute costs",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 235,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310917",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "970e937afe573ec2": {
      "id": "970e937afe573ec2",
      "text": "## Next Steps After Installation\n\n1. **Test with sample audio**\n2. **Integrate with media monitoring**\n3. **Set up auto-transcription for Telegram**\n4. **Create backup of transcripts**\n5. **Monitor disk space** (models are large)",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 243,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310930",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "7f34bcc8d1b55139": {
      "id": "7f34bcc8d1b55139",
      "text": "## Model Sizes and Requirements\n\n- **tiny:** 75 MB, works on any system\n- **base:** 142 MB, recommended default\n- **small:** 466 MB, good balance\n- **medium:** 1.5 GB, high accuracy\n- **large:** 2.9 GB, best accuracy\n\nChoose based on your accuracy needs and available RAM.",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcriber/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 252,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.310945",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "1ca7de845df55f1e": {
      "id": "1ca7de845df55f1e",
      "text": "---\nname: service-management\ndescription: \"Manage cron jobs, services, and background processes in OpenClaw. Use when: (1) Cron jobs are failing, (2) Services need configuration, (3) Background processes require management, (4) Scripts need fixing or optimization, (5) Scheduled tasks need monitoring.\"\n---\n\n# Service Management",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 7,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311020",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "ec6c35b7cd24d18a": {
      "id": "ec6c35b7cd24d18a",
      "text": "## Overview\n\nThis skill provides tools and best practices for managing scheduled tasks, services, and background processes in OpenClaw. It addresses common issues like cron job failures, service configuration problems, and process management.",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 11,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311034",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "cd39f8cdfea200f6": {
      "id": "cd39f8cdfea200f6",
      "text": "### 1. Cron Jobs\nScheduled tasks that run at specific times. Common issues:\n- PATH environment issues\n- Permission problems\n- Script errors\n- Output handling",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 20,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311045",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "b7249062fe2232b5": {
      "id": "b7249062fe2232b5",
      "text": "### 2. Systemd Services\nManaged services that can start on boot and restart on failure.",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311053",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "12509abe1177647e": {
      "id": "12509abe1177647e",
      "text": "### 3. Background Processes\nLong-running processes managed via process managers or screen/tmux.",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311061",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a2fc38646a578e64": {
      "id": "a2fc38646a578e64",
      "text": "### 4. Scheduled Tasks\nOne-time or recurring tasks scheduled via `at`, cron, or custom schedulers.",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311069",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e668499ffffc1e3d": {
      "id": "e668499ffffc1e3d",
      "text": "## Cron Job Management",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311074",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "d729d1171ae844b6": {
      "id": "d729d1171ae844b6",
      "text": "### Creating Reliable Cron Jobs\n\n**Basic Structure:**\n\n**Best Practices:**\n\n1. **Use full paths:** Cron has minimal PATH\n2. **Redirect output:** Capture stdout and stderr\n3. **Set environment:** Export needed variables\n4. **Add logging:** Log to files for debugging",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 45,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311089",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "6904d3127d9ee9ec": {
      "id": "6904d3127d9ee9ec",
      "text": "5. **Test manually:** Run command outside cron first\n\n**Example Reliable Cron Entry:**",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 53,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311098",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8551bec5cbb84d18": {
      "id": "8551bec5cbb84d18",
      "text": "### Common Cron Issues and Fixes\n\n**Issue: \"Command not found\"**\n\n**Issue: No output/errors**\n\n**Issue: Permission denied**",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 89,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311110",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4948fc2712732841": {
      "id": "4948fc2712732841",
      "text": "### Cron Management Scripts\n\n- `scripts/cron_test.py`: Test cron entries before adding\n- `scripts/cron_monitor.py`: Monitor cron job execution\n- `scripts/cron_backup.py`: Backup and restore crontab",
      "source": "skills/service-management/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 95,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.311122",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
