      "text": "### Process Monitoring Scripts\n\n- `scripts/process_monitor.py`: Monitor background processes\n- `scripts/process_cleanup.py`: Clean up zombie processes\n- `scripts/resource_monitor.py`: Monitor CPU/memory usage",
