    },
    "3f8877e4893feabb": {
      "id": "3f8877e4893feabb",
      "text": "### `scripts/venv_whisper.py`\nCreates and manages virtual environments for Whisper:",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
