    "ef47ea3f8f5c872e": {
      "id": "ef47ea3f8f5c872e",
      "text": "### 3. Create Wrapper Script",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 141,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.312988",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "5ca8af2afbf79804": {
      "id": "5ca8af2afbf79804",
      "text": "### 4. Make it Persistent\nAdd to `.bashrc` or script that activates venv on demand.",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.312996",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "af2773ffcbde7b3e": {
      "id": "af2773ffcbde7b3e",
      "text": "## Comparison of Methods\n\n| Method | Setup Complexity | Performance | Privacy | Internet Required |\n|--------|------------------|-------------|---------|-------------------|\n| Virtual Environment | Medium | Good | Excellent | No (after install) |\n| Docker | Medium | Good | Excellent | No (after pull) |\n| Whisper.cpp | Easy | Excellent | Excellent | No |\n| API | Easy | Good | Poor (data leaves) | Yes |\n| System Install | Hard (PEP 668) | Good | Excellent | No |",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 154,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313017",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a2a4ec4b7f7b82a7": {
      "id": "a2a4ec4b7f7b82a7",
      "text": "## Troubleshooting PEP 668",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 156,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313024",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "64da8f0cc7c16019": {
      "id": "64da8f0cc7c16019",
      "text": "### If `--user` fails:",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 168,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313030",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "30acdc416c04ded2": {
      "id": "30acdc416c04ded2",
      "text": "### If virtual env fails:",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 177,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313036",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e8d8e276727ab764": {
      "id": "e8d8e276727ab764",
      "text": "## Integration with OpenClaw",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313043",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c3fa1f82ae7da622": {
      "id": "c3fa1f82ae7da622",
      "text": "### Auto-Detection Script\nCreate a script that tries methods in order:",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 208,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313052",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a843b2ad659067a9": {
      "id": "a843b2ad659067a9",
      "text": "### Telegram Integration\nWhen audio is received:\n1. Check if any transcription method is available\n2. Use best available method\n3. If none, provide metadata and installation instructions",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 214,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313063",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "787e2bcf01c0b35e": {
      "id": "787e2bcf01c0b35e",
      "text": "## Minimal Viable Transcription\n\nWhen nothing else works, at least provide:\n\n1. **Audio metadata:** Duration, format, size\n2. **Conversion options:** How to convert to text manually\n3. **Installation guide:** Steps to enable transcription",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 228,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313078",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "b6ed58c98180877e": {
      "id": "b6ed58c98180877e",
      "text": "## Security Considerations",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 230,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313083",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "34f7c2b2e0927e29": {
      "id": "34f7c2b2e0927e29",
      "text": "### Virtual Environments\n- Isolated from system Python\n- Can be deleted easily\n- No root access needed",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 235,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313092",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "6abbb62c1b992800": {
      "id": "6abbb62c1b992800",
      "text": "### Docker\n- Containerized, more secure\n- Can limit resources\n- Easy to clean up",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 240,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313100",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "910c6ecaa811d4f8": {
      "id": "910c6ecaa811d4f8",
      "text": "### APIs\n- Data leaves your system\n- Check provider's privacy policy\n- Use for non-sensitive audio only",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 245,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313109",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a560700d754a3604": {
      "id": "a560700d754a3604",
      "text": "## Performance Optimization",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313114",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "417c2a8dde8579e9": {
      "id": "417c2a8dde8579e9",
      "text": "### For Virtual Environments",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 258,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313122",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "d64b7798d94c8fde": {
      "id": "d64b7798d94c8fde",
      "text": "## Reference: PEP 668 Workarounds",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313131",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "7b005d3af025026a": {
      "id": "7b005d3af025026a",
      "text": "### Official Recommendations\n1. Use virtual environments\n2. Use `pipx` for applications\n3. Use `--user` flag\n4. Use system package manager when possible",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 283,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313142",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "137c7b534c259344": {
      "id": "137c7b534c259344",
      "text": "## Emergency: Quick Transcription Needed\n\nIf you need transcription immediately and nothing is installed:\n\n1. **Convert to text manually:** Play audio and type\n2. **Use online service:** uploadfiles.io, vocaroo.com\n3. **Mobile app:** Use phone's voice-to-text\n4. **Ask for text version:** Request user to type instead\n\nThen work on proper installation for future audio.",
      "source": "skills/audio-transcription-alt/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 318,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313163",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "d946606d97ef2da9": {
      "id": "d946606d97ef2da9",
      "text": "---\nname: system-diagnostics\ndescription: \"Diagnose and troubleshoot OpenClaw system issues. Use when: (1) Services are failing (gateway, browser, cron jobs), (2) API integrations not working, (3) Logs show errors, (4) System performance issues, (5) Configuration problems need investigation.\"\n---\n\n# System Diagnostics",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 7,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313219",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c33b5c668eb968b3": {
      "id": "c33b5c668eb968b3",
      "text": "## Overview\n\nThis skill provides systematic approaches to diagnosing OpenClaw system issues. It includes checklists, scripts, and troubleshooting guides for common problems encountered in production.",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 11,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313231",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "b87f3c1f0055adf6": {
      "id": "b87f3c1f0055adf6",
      "text": "## Quick Diagnostic Checklist",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313237",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "cdebba7147d976ac": {
      "id": "cdebba7147d976ac",
      "text": "### 1. Service Status Check",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 25,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313243",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e72f7817bdbbceec": {
      "id": "e72f7817bdbbceec",
      "text": "### 2. Log Inspection",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 37,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313249",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "33805fc5a9614f32": {
      "id": "33805fc5a9614f32",
      "text": "### 3. Configuration Verification",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 46,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313255",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "929a27e376fc1e73": {
      "id": "929a27e376fc1e73",
      "text": "## Common Issue Categories",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 48,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313261",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c01cb2159f05eb6d": {
      "id": "c01cb2159f05eb6d",
      "text": "### Category 1: Gateway Issues\n\n**Symptoms:**\n- \"Cannot connect to gateway\"\n- Gateway process not running\n- Authentication failures\n\n**Diagnosis:**\n\n**Solutions:**",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 68,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313273",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "0352bcc1897fcfdb": {
      "id": "0352bcc1897fcfdb",
      "text": "- Restart gateway: `openclaw gateway restart`\n- Check firewall rules\n- Verify bind address in config",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 72,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313282",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "1bd71fdc543ab8eb": {
      "id": "1bd71fdc543ab8eb",
      "text": "### Category 2: Browser Control Issues\n\n**Symptoms:**\n- \"Profile not found\"\n- Browser not starting\n- CDP connection failures\n\n**Diagnosis:**\n\n**Solutions:**",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 92,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313294",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "2b142124af27910d": {
      "id": "2b142124af27910d",
      "text": "- Start browser with remote debugging\n- Configure correct CDP URL in profiles\n- Check browser installation",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 96,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313303",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "95c593f8c730f11d": {
      "id": "95c593f8c730f11d",
      "text": "### Category 3: API Integration Issues\n\n**Symptoms:**\n- \"401 Unauthorized\" errors\n- API calls failing\n- Rate limit errors\n\n**Diagnosis:**\n\n**Solutions:**",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 116,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313315",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "993605fe0dfdb7dc": {
      "id": "993605fe0dfdb7dc",
      "text": "- Verify API keys\n- Check rate limits\n- Update expired credentials",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 120,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313322",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "72fe25e930cd2972": {
      "id": "72fe25e930cd2972",
      "text": "### Category 4: Cron Job Issues\n\n**Symptoms:**\n- Scheduled tasks not running\n- Script errors in cron logs\n- Permission issues\n\n**Diagnosis:**\n\n**Solutions:**",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 140,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313334",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "9073e743088a2eb6": {
      "id": "9073e743088a2eb6",
      "text": "- Fix script paths (use full paths in cron)\n- Set correct permissions\n- Add error logging",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 144,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313342",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "ddc6771ff29d0106": {
      "id": "ddc6771ff29d0106",
      "text": "## Diagnostic Scripts",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 146,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313348",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "25609c02f4d4116b": {
      "id": "25609c02f4d4116b",
      "text": "### `scripts/health_check.py`\nComprehensive system health check:\n- Service status\n- Disk space\n- Memory usage\n- Log errors\n- API connectivity",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 154,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313358",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c32ee9e0fbae4824": {
      "id": "c32ee9e0fbae4824",
      "text": "### `scripts/diagnose_service.py`\nDiagnose specific service issues:\n- Gateway diagnostics\n- Browser diagnostics\n- API diagnostics",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 160,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313373",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "51a06def99b0371a": {
      "id": "51a06def99b0371a",
      "text": "### `scripts/log_analyzer.py`\nAnalyze logs for patterns:\n- Error frequency\n- Performance issues\n- Security concerns",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 166,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313382",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "89af9d08c839c9e0": {
      "id": "89af9d08c839c9e0",
      "text": "### `scripts/config_validator.py`\nValidate configuration files:\n- JSON syntax\n- Required fields\n- Value ranges",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 172,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313391",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "767ee705b456da72": {
      "id": "767ee705b456da72",
      "text": "## Real-World Examples",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 174,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313396",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4f9519baf6532353": {
      "id": "4f9519baf6532353",
      "text": "### Example 1: Moltbook Cron Failure (Today's Issue)\n**Symptoms:** 401 errors, \"openclaw: command not found\"\n\n**Diagnosis:**\n\n**Root Causes:**\n1. Script uses `openclaw` without full path\n2. Environment doesn't have PATH set in cron\n3. API key not being passed correctly",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 197,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313412",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "2cb6cb3c4e433474": {
      "id": "2cb6cb3c4e433474",
      "text": "### Example 2: Gateway Connection Issues\n**Symptoms:** entrosana.com can't connect\n\n**Diagnosis:**",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 225,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313423",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "89308b6bc33285d1": {
      "id": "89308b6bc33285d1",
      "text": "### Example 3: Browser Profile Issues\n**Symptoms:** \"Profile brave-remote not found\"\n\n**Diagnosis:**",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 240,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313432",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "d5d8f9ee69530f9e": {
      "id": "d5d8f9ee69530f9e",
      "text": "## Troubleshooting Methodology",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 242,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313438",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "dcf64c115619a911": {
      "id": "dcf64c115619a911",
      "text": "### Step 1: Reproduce the Issue\n- What exactly is failing?\n- Error messages?\n- When did it start?",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 247,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313446",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "145e80ab99aede08": {
      "id": "145e80ab99aede08",
      "text": "### Step 2: Check Basics\n- Services running?\n- Logs show errors?\n- Configuration valid?",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 252,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313454",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "70d2e68d7452a50d": {
      "id": "70d2e68d7452a50d",
      "text": "### Step 3: Isolate the Problem\n- Which component is failing?\n- Is it network, config, or code?\n- Can you reproduce manually?",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 257,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313464",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "2548c7063040d928": {
      "id": "2548c7063040d928",
      "text": "### Step 4: Test Fixes\n- Make one change at a time\n- Test after each change\n- Document what works",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 262,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313473",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "021d19c0e14b18e5": {
      "id": "021d19c0e14b18e5",
      "text": "### Step 5: Prevent Recurrence\n- Add monitoring\n- Improve error handling\n- Update documentation",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 267,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313481",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c6e1ea4f356e9d18": {
      "id": "c6e1ea4f356e9d18",
      "text": "## Prevention Strategies",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313487",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c44c4cc95cd9c2bc": {
      "id": "c44c4cc95cd9c2bc",
      "text": "### 1. Monitoring\n- Regular health checks\n- Alert on errors\n- Performance metrics",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 274,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313495",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "0eea7281b202ce34": {
      "id": "0eea7281b202ce34",
      "text": "### 2. Documentation\n- Keep runbooks updated\n- Document known issues\n- Share solutions",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 279,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313504",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "b0c74b17bfe85e88": {
      "id": "b0c74b17bfe85e88",
      "text": "### 3. Testing\n- Test configuration changes\n- Validate scripts before cron\n- Simulate failures",
