    "709be428135eb3a1": {
      "id": "709be428135eb3a1",
      "text": "## Emergency Procedures",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313550",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "3df37ef0888e1751": {
      "id": "3df37ef0888e1751",
      "text": "### Critical Issue: Gateway Down\n1. Check logs: `tail -100 /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log`\n2. Restart: `openclaw gateway restart`\n3. If fails: `openclaw gateway stop && openclaw gateway start`\n4. Check: `openclaw gateway status`",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 315,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313563",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "cf11ad86b622cff3": {
      "id": "cf11ad86b622cff3",
      "text": "### Critical Issue: API Keys Expired\n1. Identify which API is failing\n2. Check credential files\n3. Test with new keys\n4. Update configuration",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 321,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313573",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8310f8c738dc02d7": {
      "id": "8310f8c738dc02d7",
      "text": "### Critical Issue: Disk Full\n1. Check: `df -h`\n2. Clean logs: `find /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/logs -name \"*.log\" -mtime +7 -delete`\n3. Clear temp files\n4. Expand disk if needed",
      "source": "skills/system-diagnostics/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 326,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313585",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4c49dc73686d0de6": {
      "id": "4c49dc73686d0de6",
      "text": "---\nname: code-generation-analysis\ndescription: \"Code generation and analysis skill - automated code review, generation, refactoring, and bug detection\"\ntrigger: \"code\"\n---\n\n# Code Generation & Analysis Skill",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 8,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313653",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "2a3e59bf78400154": {
      "id": "2a3e59bf78400154",
      "text": "## Overview\n\nA comprehensive code skill for generating, analyzing, reviewing, and refactoring code across multiple programming languages. Uses multi-model orchestration for specialized code tasks.",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 12,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313665",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c2641e468f40bea2": {
      "id": "c2641e468f40bea2",
      "text": "## Trigger Phrases\n\nThe skill activates when messages contain:\n- \"code\" (as verb: \"code X\", \"generate code for Y\")\n- \"write code\"\n- \"review code\"\n- \"analyze code\"\n- \"refactor\"\n- \"debug\"\n- \"fix code\"",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 22,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313679",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "221c4f0bc8b2a6bb": {
      "id": "221c4f0bc8b2a6bb",
      "text": "- \"implement\"\n- \"develop\"\n- \"program\"",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 26,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313695",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "41cc17aff81a7040": {
      "id": "41cc17aff81a7040",
      "text": "### 2. Model Coordination\n- **Planning Phase:** claude-sonnet (reasoning + planning)\n- **Generation Phase:** gpt-4 (creativity + coding)\n- **Analysis Phase:** llama-code (specialized coding)\n- **Review Phase:** claude-sonnet (review + security)\n- **Optimization Phase:** gpt-4 (performance + best practices)",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 40,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313715",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "fc875dc11a2b3998": {
      "id": "fc875dc11a2b3998",
      "text": "### 3. Supported Languages\n- **Primary:** Python, JavaScript/TypeScript, Java, C++, Go, Rust\n- **Web:** HTML/CSS, React, Vue, Angular\n- **Scripting:** Bash, PowerShell, SQL\n- **Configuration:** YAML, JSON, XML, Dockerfile, Kubernetes",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 46,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313729",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e1828fadc69fafc5": {
      "id": "e1828fadc69fafc5",
      "text": "### Core Components\n\n1. **`code_skill.py`** - Main skill handler\n2. **`code_generator.py`** - Code generation with templates\n3. **`code_analyzer.py`** - Static analysis and review\n4. **`code_refactorer.py`** - Refactoring and optimization\n5. **`language_detector.py`** - Programming language identification",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 90,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313751",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "1bf43a10f628394c": {
      "id": "1bf43a10f628394c",
      "text": "### Integration Points\n\n- **Multi-Model Orchestrator** - Coordinates AI models for code tasks\n- **Research Skill** - For researching coding patterns and best practices\n- **Async Agent Pattern** - Long-running code analysis tasks\n- **Memory System** - Store and retrieve code patterns and solutions",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 97,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313766",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "0420bba3d6889b78": {
      "id": "0420bba3d6889b78",
      "text": "### 1. Requirements Analysis\n- Parse code requirements\n- Identify language and framework\n- Determine complexity level\n- Set quality standards",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 105,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313777",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "fb7722d428cdf7fa": {
      "id": "fb7722d428cdf7fa",
      "text": "### 2. Code Generation Process\n- Template selection\n- Pattern application\n- Best practices integration\n- Documentation generation",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 111,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313787",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "be4cc97ae6e85b69": {
      "id": "be4cc97ae6e85b69",
      "text": "### 3. Analysis & Review\n- Static code analysis\n- Security vulnerability scanning\n- Performance benchmarking\n- Style consistency checking\n- Dependency analysis",
