    "0c2c3382d235279b": {
      "id": "0c2c3382d235279b",
      "text": "### Analysis Depth\n1. **Quick** - Surface-level issues only\n2. **Standard** - Comprehensive analysis\n3. **Deep** - In-depth with performance profiling\n4. **Security** - Focus on vulnerabilities and threats",
