    "b790dc146ad25e19": {
      "id": "b790dc146ad25e19",
      "text": "### Project Integration\n- Link to thesis coding projects\n- Track code quality over time\n- Generate documentation\n- Maintain code standards",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
