      ]
    },
    "d17d6fa77b0df8d7": {
      "id": "d17d6fa77b0df8d7",
      "text": "### Development Pipeline\n1. **Planning** → Requirements analysis\n2. **Generation** → Initial implementation\n3. **Review** → Quality assurance\n4. **Refactoring** → Optimization\n5. **Documentation** → Knowledge transfer",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 258,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313907",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "46f57942ca87c320": {
      "id": "46f57942ca87c320",
      "text": "### Heartbeat Integration\nCode tasks can be scheduled via heartbeat for:\n- Daily code reviews\n- Weekly refactoring sessions\n- Ongoing project development\n- Security scanning",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 265,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313920",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "766b67550b83e349": {
      "id": "766b67550b83e349",
      "text": "### Validation Methods\n1. **Syntax checking** - Ensure code compiles/parses\n2. **Test generation** - Create unit tests\n3. **Edge case analysis** - Test boundary conditions\n4. **Performance testing** - Benchmark execution\n5. **Security scanning** - Vulnerability detection",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 274,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313936",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "4a1aa572250c34ca": {
      "id": "4a1aa572250c34ca",
      "text": "### Confidence Scoring\n- **High (0.8-1.0)** - Well-tested patterns, multiple validation passes\n- **Medium (0.5-0.8)** - Generally correct, some uncertainty\n- **Low (0.0-0.5)** - Experimental, needs manual review",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 279,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313949",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "b41f17ebb47586aa": {
      "id": "b41f17ebb47586aa",
      "text": "### Current Constraints\n1. **No execution** - Cannot run generated code (safety)\n2. **Limited context** - Large codebases may be challenging\n3. **Language support** - Some niche languages limited\n4. **Framework knowledge** - Rapidly evolving frameworks",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 287,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313964",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "171118b4734210d4": {
      "id": "171118b4734210d4",
      "text": "### Mitigation Strategies\n- Focus on core language features\n- Provide clear requirements\n- Break large tasks into smaller ones\n- Use established patterns and templates",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 293,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313975",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "589759599796cee2": {
      "id": "589759599796cee2",
      "text": "## Future Enhancements",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
