    "e491db912a646ebd": {
      "id": "e491db912a646ebd",
      "text": "### Planned Features\n1. **Live code execution** - Safe sandbox for testing\n2. **Learning from corrections** - Improve based on feedback\n3. **Code pattern library** - Reusable templates and solutions\n4. **Collaborative coding** - Pair programming simulation\n5. **Project scaffolding** - Complete project generation",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 302,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.313996",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "93a5b1fa1ad5e3c8": {
      "id": "93a5b1fa1ad5e3c8",
      "text": "### Integration Goals\n1. **IDE integration** - Direct editor support\n2. **CI/CD pipeline** - Automated code review\n3. **Version control** - Git integration\n4. **Team collaboration** - Multi-developer support",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 308,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314009",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "90825d861e1de822": {
      "id": "90825d861e1de822",
      "text": "### Best Practices\n1. **Be specific** - Clear requirements yield better code\n2. **Provide context** - Include existing code when relevant\n3. **Set standards** - Specify quality/security requirements\n4. **Iterate** - Start simple, then enhance",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 316,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314023",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "941be1b62c903889": {
      "id": "941be1b62c903889",
      "text": "### Common Use Cases\n- Prototype development\n- Code review and auditing\n- Learning and education\n- Legacy code modernization\n- Interview preparation\n- Open source contribution",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 324,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314035",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "1c0b9ae9481782c6": {
      "id": "1c0b9ae9481782c6",
      "text": "### Basic Usage\nJust say \"code [what]\" and the skill will automatically:\n1. Analyze your requirements\n2. Determine appropriate language and approach\n3. Generate or analyze code\n4. Return results with documentation",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 333,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314048",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "123fa8f8a3bcd527": {
      "id": "123fa8f8a3bcd527",
      "text": "### Advanced Usage\nFor more control, specify:\n- \"review code: [code snippet]\" - Code analysis\n- \"refactor: [code]\" - Optimization\n- \"debug: [problem description]\" - Bug finding\n- \"implement [feature] in [language]\" - Specific generation",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 340,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314062",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "7562d41f634e1bd6": {
      "id": "7562d41f634e1bd6",
      "text": "### Integration with Other Skills\n- Use with **research skill** for coding pattern research\n- Use with **multi-model orchestrator** for complex tasks\n- Use with **async pattern** for long-running analysis\n- Use for **crypto skill** development (smart contracts, etc.)",
      "source": "skills/code-generation-analysis/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 345,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314076",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
