    "cf4aa447b7612b2d": {
      "id": "cf4aa447b7612b2d",
      "text": "## Specialist Agent Routing Table\n\nAdapted from Intent Agent Starter Kit for OpenClaw ACP:\n\n| Domain | Specialist Agent | ACP Provider | When to Use |\n|--------|------------------|--------------|-------------|\n| **Architecture** | Lead Architect | Claude Code | System design, tech selection, ADRs |\n| **Product** | Product Owner | Claude Code | PRDs, feature specs, user stories |\n| **Testing** | QA Engineer | Claude Code | Test execution, coverage (Gate 3) |\n| **Research** | Research Analyst | Claude Code + EXA | Technology research, competitive analysis |",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 174,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314677",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "33da36f805eec167": {
      "id": "33da36f805eec167",
      "text": "| **Risk** | Devil's Advocate | Claude Code | Risk review, assumption testing (Gate 1) |\n| **Security** | Security Specialist | Claude Code | Vulnerability audit, OWASP review (Gate 2) |\n| **Code Audit** | Code Auditor | Claude Code | Spec vs implementation comparison (Gate 2) |\n| **UX** | UX Strategist | Claude Code | User research, interaction design |\n| **Docs** | Technical Writer | Claude Code | API docs, guides, documentation |\n| **DevOps** | DevOps Engineer | Claude Code | CI/CD, deployment, infrastructure |\n| **Performance** | Performance Engineer | Claude Code | Optimization, profiling, metrics |\n| **Code Quality** | Code Simplifier | Claude Code | Complexity reduction, readability |\n| **Design System** | Design Systems Specialist | Claude Code | Design tokens, component library |\n| **Mobile** | Mobile Developer | Claude Code | React Native / Expo implementation |",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 184,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314726",
