    },
    "0505d67b40bd90ce": {
      "id": "0505d67b40bd90ce",
      "text": "### 1. **Token Efficiency**\n- Use smaller models for routing and classification tasks\n- Cache repeated tool calls and LLM responses\n- Implement context pruning between agent handoffs\n- Set token budgets per agent per task",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 434,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314888",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a12cfacff2e84444": {
      "id": "a12cfacff2e84444",
      "text": "### 2. **Parallel Execution**",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 448,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314896",
      "embedding_shape": [
