    },
    "0a3d5ed50d2308b6": {
      "id": "0a3d5ed50d2308b6",
      "text": "## Security Considerations",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314908",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "6516a1076c56c7ee": {
      "id": "6516a1076c56c7ee",
      "text": "### 1. **API Key Management**\n- Store keys in environment variables, not in code\n- Use key rotation for production deployments\n- Implement rate limiting per API key\n- Monitor for unusual usage patterns",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 473,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314920",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "105acdcbd269f7a8": {
      "id": "105acdcbd269f7a8",
      "text": "### 2. **Session Isolation**\n- Each ACP session runs isolated from others\n- Clear session state between tasks\n- Implement session timeout policies\n- Log session activities for audit trails",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 479,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314931",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "23a0bf27e65433b8": {
      "id": "23a0bf27e65433b8",
      "text": "### 3. **Content Safety**\n- Validate all agent outputs against safety guidelines\n- Implement content filtering for user-facing outputs\n- Monitor for prompt injection attempts\n- Regular security reviews of agent prompts",
      "source": "skills/acp-agent-protocol-enhanced/SKILL.md",
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 485,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T18:58:04.314944",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
